---
const aboutImage = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551836022-d5d88e9218df?q=80&w=900&auto=format&fit=crop";
---

<section id="sobre-mi" class="sobre">
  <div class="sobre-inner">
    <!-- Sticky image column -->
    <div class="sobre-visual">
      <div class="visual-frame">
        <img src={aboutImage} alt="Lucía en su consulta" decoding="async" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="visual-offset" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <!-- Floating chapter indicator -->
      <div class="chapter-ring" aria-hidden="true">
        <span>01</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scrolling text column -->
    <div class="sobre-content">
      <span class="type-eyebrow reveal">Sobre mí</span>

      <h2 class="sobre-title reveal">
        <span class="type-display">No estás rota,</span>
        <span class="type-display accent">estás respondiendo</span>
        <span class="type-display">a lo que te pasó.</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="sobre-chapters">
        <div class="chapter reveal">
          <span class="chapter-num">I.</span>
          <p class="text-lead">
            Soy psicóloga colegiada y especialista en trauma y procesos de cambio. Mi trabajo consiste en acompañarte a sanar lo que duele, entender lo que confunde y recuperar el rumbo cuando todo parece fragmentado.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="chapter reveal">
          <span class="chapter-num">II.</span>
          <p>
            Formada en terapia cognitivo-conductual y certificada en EMDR —una de las terapias con mayor evidencia científica para el tratamiento del trauma—, combino técnicas estructuradas con un abordaje profundamente humano y cercano.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="chapter reveal">
          <span class="chapter-num">III.</span>
          <p>
            Creo firmemente en la capacidad de recuperación de cada persona. No busco "arreglarte", sino ayudarte a reconectar con tus propios recursos.
          </p>
          <a href="#contacto" class="btn-ghost">Hablemos de ti →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scattered floating stats -->
  <div class="floating-stats">
    <div class="f-stat stat-a reveal">
      <span class="f-num">8+</span>
      <span class="f-label">Años de<br/>experiencia</span>
    </div>
    <div class="f-stat stat-b reveal">
      <span class="f-num">500+</span>
      <span class="f-label">Pacientes<br/>acompañadas</span>
    </div>
    <div class="f-stat stat-c reveal">
      <span class="f-num">EMDR</span>
      <span class="f-label">Certificación<br/>internacional</span>
    </div>
    <!-- Decorative line -->
    <div class="f-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .sobre {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 10rem 0 12rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .sobre-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 6vw;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* Sticky visual */
  .sobre-visual {
    position: sticky;
    top: 120px;
    height: fit-content;
    align-self: start;
  }
  .visual-frame {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(42,31,26,0.1);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .visual-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.8s var(--ease-out-expo);
  }
  .visual-frame:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }
  .visual-offset {
    position: absolute;
    top: 18px; left: 18px;
    right: -18px; bottom: -18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--mint);
    border-radius: 3px;
    opacity: 0.25;
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .chapter-ring {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -30px;
    right: -30px;
    width: 80px; height: 80px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 3;
    background: var(--cream);
  }
  .chapter-ring span {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--taupe);
  }

  /* Content */
  .sobre-content {
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }
  .sobre-content .type-eyebrow {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .sobre-title {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  .sobre-title .type-display {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.8vw, 3.5rem);
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .sobre-title .accent {
    color: var(--taupe);
  }

  .sobre-chapters {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }
  .chapter {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 3.5rem;
  }
  .chapter-num {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--taupe);
    opacity: 0.35;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .text-lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.7vw, 1.35rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .chapter p:not(.text-lead) {
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* Floating stats */
  .floating-stats {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 8rem auto 0;
    padding: 0 6vw;
    height: 300px;
  }
  .f-stat {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .stat-a { top: 0; left: 6vw; }
  .stat-b { top: 60px; left: 35%; }
  .stat-c { top: 20px; right: 6vw; }
  .f-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--taupe);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .f-label {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--taupe);
    opacity: 0.6;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .f-line {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 80px;
    left: 15%;
    right: 15%;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--line);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .sobre-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
    .sobre-visual {
      position: relative;
      top: auto;
      max-width: 400px;
    }
    .floating-stats {
      height: auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 3rem;
      margin-top: 5rem;
    }
    .f-stat {
      position: relative;
      top: auto; left: auto; right: auto;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .f-line { display: none; }
  }
</style>
